<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>TripManager</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="logo">TripManager</div>
    <input type="text" class="search-bar" placeholder="어디로 떠나시나요?">
    <div class="auth-btns">
        <% if (user) { %>
            <span><%= user.name %>님 환영합니다!</span>
            <a href="/mypage" class="btn-blue">내 정보</a>
            <a href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a>
        <% } else { %>
            <a href="/auth/join">회원가입</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn-blue">로그인</a>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="/reserve/international">해외 숙소</a>
    <a href="/reserve/domestic">국내 숙소</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>여행 호텔 결정은 TripManager와 함께!</h1>
</div>

</body>
</html>